OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FThe majority of college staff want
OL,7,FOfsted inspections to be abolished, a
OL,8,Fsurvey has suggested.
OL,10,FA poll of more than 1,000 University
OL,11,Fand College Union (UCU) members in the
OL,12,Ffurther education (FE) sector suggests
OL,13,Fnearly four in five (77%) believe the
OL,14,FOfsted term "inadequate" is
OL,15,Funacceptable.
