OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FOfsted inspections create a "major
OL,7,Fhealth and safety risk" for staff who
OL,8,Fexperience significant levels of
OL,9,Fstress and anxiety as a result of the
OL,10,Fprocess, according to a report from
OL,11,Fthe union.
OL,13,FThe watchdog has come under greater
OL,14,Fscrutiny in the past year following
OL,15,Fthe death of headteacher Ruth Perry.
