OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FMs Perry took her own life after an
OL,7,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,8,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,9,Fhighest rating, "outstanding", to its
OL,10,Flowest rating, "inadequate", over
OL,11,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,13,FIn December, a coroner concluded the
OL,14,FOfsted inspection on November 15 and
OL,15,F16 in 2022 "contributed" to Mrs
OL,16,FPerry's death.
OL,18,FThe survey of UCU members in FE in
OL,19,FEngland, carried out between July and
OL,20,FSeptember 2023, found 57% believe
OL,21,FOfsted inspections should be abolished.
