OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FMore than four in five (83%) said
OL,7,FOfsted inspections cause them anxiety
OL,8,Fand only 20% said they believe the
OL,9,FOfsted inspection process raises
OL,10,Fstandards.
OL,12,FIn March, Sir Martyn Oliver, chief
OL,13,Finspector of Ofsted, launched the
OL,14,Fwatchdog's Big Listen public
OL,15,Fconsultation ` which closes at the end
OL,16,Fof the month ` to seek views about the
OL,17,Finspectorate.
