OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FLast week, the Department for
OL,7,FEducation (DfE) said it had no plans
OL,8,Fto remove single-phrase Ofsted
OL,9,Fjudgments despite calls for them to be
OL,10,Fscrapped.
OL,12,FIn its response to an Education Select
OL,13,FCommittee inquiry on Ofsted, the DfE
OL,14,Fsaid its priority was to look for ways
OL,15,Fto improve the inspection system
OL,16,Frather than "developing an alternative
OL,17,Fto it".
