OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FThe report from the UCU ` on Ofsted
OL,7,Finspection in the FE sector `
OL,8,Frecommends that Ofsted inspections
OL,9,Fshould be replaced with a
OL,10,Fcollaborative peer-to-peer model that
OL,11,Fis valued and trusted by staff,
OL,12,Fstudents and parents.
OL,14,FIt said: "The findings of this
OL,15,Fresearch show that, overall, UCU
OL,16,Fmembers have grave concerns about the
OL,17,Fstress, anxiety and adverse impact on
OL,18,Fhealth and wellbeing they experience
OL,19,Fas a result of Ofsted inspections and
OL,20,Fpreparation for an Ofsted inspection.
