OL,6,F"Our findings show that Ofsted
OL,7,Finspections create a major health and
OL,8,Fsafety risk for staff who experience
OL,9,Fsignificant levels of stress and
OL,10,Fanxiety both during and in the lead-up
OL,11,Fto inspections."
OL,13,FThe report added: "There is a crisis
OL,14,Fof confidence in the Ofsted inspection
OL,15,Fprocess."
