OL,3,CMajority of college staff want Ofsted
OL,4,Cinspections to be abolished ` survey
OL,6,FUCU general secretary Jo Grady said:
OL,7,F"College staff are clear that Ofsted
OL,8,Finspections need to be abolished. Our
OL,9,Fmembers say inspections are traumatic,
OL,10,Fand especially after the tragic death
OL,11,Fof Ruth Perry, we need an end to the
OL,12,Fstress and anxiety they induce.
OL,14,F"This report also affirms that the
OL,15,Fcase for scrapping the 'inadequate'
OL,16,Fruling is incontrovertible. It is
OL,17,Fsimply unacceptable for the Government
OL,18,Fto rule out replacing it before
OL,19,FOfsted's consultation has even
OL,20,Ffinished.
