OL,6,F"We now need an end to the tyranny of
OL,7,FOfsted inspections and for the health
OL,8,Fand safety of staff to be properly
OL,9,Fincorporated into a new peer-to-peer
OL,10,Fled model that is valued by those who
OL,11,Factually work in the sector."
OL,13,FSir Martyn will address hundreds of
OL,14,Fschool leaders at the NAHT annual
OL,15,Fconference in Newport in Wales this
OL,16,Fweekend.
OL,18,FDelegates at the school leaders' union
OL,19,Fconference are due to debate a series
OL,20,Fof motions on inspection and
OL,21,Faccountability on Saturday.
